---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/page.css";

// Welcome to Astro! Wondering what to do next? Check out the Astro documentation at https://docs.astro.build
// Don't want to use any of this? Delete everything in this file, the `assets`, `components`, and `layouts` directories, and start fresh.
---

<Layout>
	<section class="page">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="page-intro">
				<span class="page-eyebrow"> About MonkeyReach </span>

				<h1 class="page-title">
					Data-Driven Digital Marketing Built Around Business Growth
				</h1>

				<p class="page-description">
					MonkeyReach Media is an MSME-registered digital marketing
					agency based in Kurukshetra, Haryana. We help businesses
					grow through SEO, paid advertising, web development, local
					marketing, content strategy, and performance-focused digital
					solutions—all backed by research instead of assumptions.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="page-content">
				<section class="page-card">
					<h2>MonkeyReach at a Glance</h2>

					<ul>
						<li>
							<strong>MSME Registered Agency</strong> — Officially registered
							under the Government of India's Udyam MSME program.
						</li>

						<li>
							<strong>6+ Years of Industry Experience</strong> — Practical
							experience across digital marketing, SEO, web technologies,
							analytics, automation, and business growth.
						</li>

						<li>
							<strong>22-Metric Business Framework</strong> — Every
							strategy begins with structured business qualification
							before any recommendation is made.
						</li>

						<li>
							<strong>Performance-Focused Marketing</strong> — Every
							campaign is designed around measurable business outcomes,
							not vanity metrics.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="page-section">
					<h2>Our Story</h2>

					<p>
						MonkeyReach Media was founded with one simple belief:
						digital marketing decisions should be supported by
						evidence, not sales pitches. Instead of recommending
						services first, we begin by understanding the business
						itself—its economics, customers, competition, and
						long-term growth potential.
					</p>

					<p>
						What started as an SEO-focused practice has evolved into
						a full-service digital marketing agency offering search
						engine optimisation, Google Ads, social media marketing,
						local SEO, website development, content strategy,
						analytics, and growth consulting.
					</p>

					<p>
						In February 2026, MonkeyReach Media became an officially
						registered MSME (Udyam) micro-enterprise in India,
						reinforcing our commitment to building long-term
						partnerships based on transparency, measurable
						performance, and continuous improvement.
					</p>
				</section>

				<div class="page-divider"></div>

				<section class="page-section">
					<h2>How We Work</h2>

					<p>
						Every client engagement follows a structured process
						designed to remove uncertainty and maximise return on
						investment.
					</p>

					<ol>
						<li>
							Business qualification using our proprietary
							22-metric framework.
						</li>

						<li>Market research and competitor analysis.</li>

						<li>Customer and search intent evaluation.</li>

						<li>Technical website and marketing audit.</li>

						<li>
							Growth strategy across the most suitable digital
							channels.
						</li>

						<li>
							Transparent implementation with measurable
							reporting.
						</li>
					</ol>

					<p>
						Whether the solution involves SEO, paid advertising,
						website improvements, content marketing, or local
						visibility, recommendations are based on data—not
						assumptions.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="page-section">
					<h2>Our Services</h2>

					<p>
						MonkeyReach Media provides integrated digital marketing
						solutions that work together to help businesses attract,
						convert, and retain customers.
					</p>

					<ul>
						<li>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</li>

						<li>Local SEO</li>

						<li>Google Ads (PPC)</li>

						<li>Social Media Marketing</li>

						<li>Website Design & Development</li>

						<li>Conversion Rate Optimisation</li>

						<li>Content Strategy</li>

						<li>Analytics & Reporting</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="page-card">
					<h2>Meet the Founder</h2>

					<h3>Sahil Raajput</h3>

					<p>
						MonkeyReach Media is currently founder-led, meaning
						every client works directly with the person responsible
						for research, strategy, execution, and continuous
						optimisation. There are no unnecessary layers of
						communication or outsourced decision-making.
					</p>

					<p>
						Every recommendation is built around the same analytical
						framework used to evaluate each business, ensuring
						strategies remain commercially focused rather than
						trend-driven.
					</p>

					<blockquote>
						I founded MonkeyReach with one principle: every
						marketing investment should be supported by research,
						measurable outcomes, and genuine business value—not
						guesswork.
					</blockquote>
				</section>

				<section class="page-card text-center">
					<h2>Let's Build Sustainable Growth</h2>

					<p>
						Whether you're looking to improve search visibility,
						generate qualified leads, build a better website, or
						scale your digital presence, MonkeyReach Media combines
						research, strategy, and execution to help your business
						grow with confidence.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
